clan and to immortal declaring your intention to mutiny and 3
supporters, you or one of your supports must have attained a rank of at
least /3.  At this point all recruiters will be demoted and each player in
the clan may vote for the person whom they think should lead the robe.
Votes will be tallied by immortal and the voting shall last for 1 week.
The loser of the vote will be ranked /0 and all of their valuables will
be handed over to the victor.  The future of the loser in the clan is left
in the hands of the victor.

{RDemise{x

