0 RESTRING RESTRINGS~
none~
0 1 none
A restring is a service offered by Immortals to players who ask politely.
A restring allows you to rename an item in your possession.

Before you get a restring there are a few things you need to make sure you
have first:

i) 1 shard for a standard restring, 2 shards for a restring with color,
   or a restring certificate of some sort
ii) the item you wish to restring
iii) the short and long description of the item you wish to have restrung

Once you have all of these things you can ask an immortal (level 55+) if they 
would be willing to do one for you.  You will be asked to provide the short
description and long description (and in some cases the keywords, or name)
of the item. The keywords you choose must be in both the long and short
descriptions you provide.

A short description is what you see when and item is in a shop, being worn,
or in your inventory.  A long description is what you see when an item is
either examined/looked at, or on the ground.

For example:
short description: a sub issue shield
long description: You see a sub issue shield here.
keywors: sub issue shield   


1)    The keywords you choose *MUST* exist in both the long and short
      descriptions.  If there is more than one key, you may have one
      key in the short description, and a different one in the long
      description, so long both long and short have a keyword in them.

2)    Several different objects may not be restrung with the exact same
      name.  This means at the same time or over time.  Objects found to
      be intentionally restrung with duplicate names will be confiscated.

3)    You may not include the name of another character in the restring
      of an item without the express consent of that character.

4)    Containers must be restrung to something that resembles a container
      in some fashion.  Be creative, but no restringing "a bag" into "a
      shoe".

5)    There is no discount for multiple restrings at the same time.  The
      pricing listed above is very reasonable. 

When an Immortal does a restring for you it is polite to pay attention to
what they are saying and it is always a good idea to know what you want
before you ask for a restring (unless you have prior arrangements with that
immortal), to avoid causing an Immortal unnecessary trouble.  If you follow
the directions given above your experiences with recieving restrings should
be wonderful, memorable experiences.
~
